Authorize file transfer and debugging on your mobile
(https://reactnative.dev/docs/running-on-device)

in terminals 1 and 2:
cd POLIME

in terminal 1: 
npx react-native start


in terminal 2: 
adb -s 13161JEC203853 reverse tcp:8081 tcp:8081
("13161JEC203853" is the ID of my mobile ONLY)

in terminal 2: 
npx react-native run-android